==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionDecreaseDecimal''' tool decreases the number of decimal places of the dimension text.

==Usage==

# Select one or more dimensions.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDecreaseDecimal.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionDecreaseDecimal|Decrease Decimal Places]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Dimensions → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDecreaseDecimal.svg|16px]] Decrease Decimal Places}} option from the menu.
# The number of decimal places of the selected dimensions is decreased by one.

==Notes==

* The minimum number of decimal places is 0.


